      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used; bovine blood properties are an accepted surrogate for human blood in hemolysis studies. Five operating points span the COU envelope for flow rate and speed. Validation activities are considered relevant to the COU at MRL 2. Environmental operating conditions of the deployment setting (temperature range, EM environment, altitude) were not part of the validation scope and no bounding argument has been provided."
